{"tid":1631514,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【警告】極大量5毛出分化Post","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:37:34.000Z","uid":49669,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d2645859d8210ab7504146e90fd912c7891fa368","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"發覺呢2日極大量5毛出分化Post，事無大小都話要割割割割割割割割割割割<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">割你老母啊！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">核爆都唔割啊！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府最鍾意就係玩分化，大家千祈唔好中計~<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記咁多手足既犧牲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港！！！時代革命！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2946c822de200787210a58c82320ea729d7232","tid":1631514,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:11.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"113128aedf06358fb32d42bc3294ff09fc754cb6","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b26165481250f6127f188a58740d170cf393ffe9","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"562337f34e91214437247628e3dd8aaba445c09f","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa027941615d9a5c70171908dcde8aa069f421be","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41874995c24bb989d87a4c8fea270d213a6e761a","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635509a22fb3c086d825be236bb32f26240cdb75","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ae61b85da20156aa4b158eb5e33d9a49f82ff1","tid":1631514,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c545fb26671dd48b43feae1fefbb3eb252d7e5c7","tid":1631514,"uid"